header: Test vectors of type JsonWebSignature are intended for tests that check the
verification operation of a JSON Web Signature library.

notes.JsonSerialization: The JWE/JWS is encoded with JSON serialization instead of compact serialization.
notes.ModifiedPadding: The PKCS #1 padding of the signature has been modified.
notes.WrongPrimitive: The signature uses a different algorithm than the algorithm specified in the key.
notes.AlgIsNone: Algorithm none must not be accepted by default.
